<span id="freeTextContainer9642601553497278403"><strong>A Cabal that controls nuclear bombs.</strong><br/><br/>In this mystery, we learn a Canal has taken control of the nuclear power of the world. Follow Morgan as he tries to stop them. This book will teach you and intrigue you. You will learn more than you might want to know and be scared at how easily it was all done. Quite an interesting read.</span>

